```
void MainWindow::paintEvent(QPaintEvent * e)  //这是一个绘画事件
{
    //界面的宽度和高度
    int width = this->width();
    int height = this->height();
    int side = qMin(width, height);

    int iScale = (side/200) + 0.5;
    
    qDebug()<<" width = "<<width<<"  height = "<<height<<"  side = "<<side<<" iScale = "<<iScale;

    //绘制准备工作,启用反锯齿,平移坐标轴中心,等比例缩放
    QPainter painter(this);
    painter.setRenderHints(QPainter::Antialiasing | QPainter::TextAntialiasing); //渲染设置
    painter.translate(width / 2, height / 2);  //按给定偏移量平移坐标系。
    painter.scale(iScale,iScale);              //缩放比例 绘图会随着界面的长宽变化而缩放

    //外边框
    int radius = 50;
    painter.save();  //save 和  restore 要成对
    painter.setPen(Qt::NoPen);
    
    QLinearGradient borderGradient(0, -radius, 0, radius); //线性渐变
    QColor borderOutColorStart = QColor(255, 255, 255);
    QColor borderOutColorEnd = QColor(166, 166, 166);
    borderGradient.setColorAt(0, borderOutColorStart);  //设置渐变点  [0,1]  可以0.3 0.5
    borderGradient.setColorAt(1, borderOutColorEnd);

    painter.setBrush(borderGradient); //设置笔刷
    painter.drawEllipse(-radius, -radius, radius * 2, radius * 2); //画椭圆
    painter.restore();

    //内边框
    radius = 45;
    painter.save();
    painter.setPen(Qt::NoPen);

    QLinearGradient borderGradient2(0, -radius, 0, radius);
    QColor borderInColorStart = QColor(166, 166, 166);
    QColor borderInColorEnd = QColor(255, 255, 255);
    borderGradient2.setColorAt(0, borderInColorStart);
    borderGradient2.setColorAt(1, borderInColorEnd);

    painter.setBrush(borderGradient2);
    painter.drawEllipse(-radius, -radius, radius * 2, radius * 2);
    painter.restore();
}
```

**绘画之线性渐变的过度区域**  

线性渐变的构造函数是这样的   
```
QLinearGradient(qreal x1, qreal y1, qreal x2, qreal y2),  (x1,y1) 过渡开始点  (x2,y2)是过渡结束点
```  
这两个点之间的范围是颜色的过渡，两个点之外的都是纯色,如果没有设置颜色，那么默认是黑白色
